function ordinalNumber(dirtyNumber) {
  var number = Number(dirtyNumber)
  var rem100 = number % 100
  if (rem100 < 20) {
    switch (rem100) {
      case 1:
      case 8:
        return number + 'ste'
      default:
        return number + 'de'
    }
  }
  return number + 'ste'
}
